  <brief_title>Single High Dose Vitamin C, E in Severe Birth Asphyxia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Single High Dose Vitamin E and Vitamin C in Hypoxic Ischemic Encephalopathy (Following Birth Asphyxia)in Newborns</official_title>
  <sponsors>
